# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok wachovia , one of america 's biggest banking groups , said monday that its chief executive ken thompson was leaving the bank at the request of the company 's board of directors .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / group
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Wachovia")
            :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                  :ARG2 (g2 / group
                        :mod (b / bank)
                        :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (b2 / big)
                              :ARG3 (m / most)
                              :ARG5 (g3 / group
                                    :mod (b3 / bank)
                                    :location (c / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "America")))))))
      :ARG1 (l / leave-11
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Ken"
                        :op2 "Thompson")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 g
                        :ARG2 (e / executive
                              :mod (c2 / chief))))
            :ARG1 (b4 / bank)
            :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (r / request-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG0-of h2
                        :ARG1 b4
                        :ARG2 (b5 / board
                              :mod (d / director))))
            :ARG1 l)
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

            :ARG0 (d / drop-01
                  :ARG1 (e / export-01

                  :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                        :ARG0 (d2 / dollar
                              :mod c
                              :ARG1-of (s2 / strong-02))
                        :degree (l2 / large))))
      :ARG1-of (s3 / say-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG0-of (m / manufacture-01)
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (b / big)
                  :ARG3 (m2 / most)
                  :ARG5 c))
      :time (s4 / since
            :op1 (d3 / date-entity
                  :month 11)))
